graph TD
    accTitle: Pre-alignment Workflow
    accDescr: Pipeline flow taking raw FASTQ files through trimming and merging before downstream alignment.

    raw_fastqs[📦 **Raw** FASTQs] --> fastp_pe[⚙️ **fastp_pe** process]
    fastp_pe --> is_multiple{**Multiple** lanes?}
    is_multiple -- Yes --> cat_fastqs[⚙️ **merged** cat FASTQs]
    is_multiple -- No --> final_fastqs
    cat_fastqs --> final_fastqs[📦 **final** merged FASTQs]
    
    final_fastqs -.-> alignment_module{{🔗 **Alignment** module}}

    fastp_pe --> qc_reports[📝 **fastp** QC reports]
    qc_reports -.-> qc_module{{🔗 **QC** module}}

    classDef primary fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,stroke-width:2px,color:#1e3a5f
    classDef success fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,stroke-width:2px,color:#14532d
    classDef warm fill:#ffedd5,stroke:#ea580c,stroke-width:2px,color:#7c2d12
    classDef accent fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:2px,color:#3b0764

    class raw_fastqs primary
    class final_fastqs success
    class qc_reports warm
    class alignment_module,qc_module accent
